1.title: Great Endeavors
1.plot: Season Two of Around the Verse begins here. This week, Community Manager Jared Huckaby sits down with Lead Writer David Haddock to discuss writing for Star Citizen and Squadron 42. Lisa Ohanian chats with Matt Sherman about continuing work on the Ship Item System in Ship Shape, and Ben Lesnick takes us Behind the Scenes on the Endeavor Science Vessel pod development.

2.title: Road to CitizenCon 2015
2.plot: Explosions. We talk explosion effects with Matthew Intrieri, go Behind the Scenes of the Drake Caterpillar with Randy Vasquez, and check in with studios around the world.

3.title: From Manchester with Love
3.plot: It's a short one coming off CitizenCon, but there's still plenty to enjoy. This week, Sandi Gardiner and Erin Roberts host while our very own Thomas Hennessy interviews Tom Johnson in the UK.

4.title: The Next Great Alpha
4.plot: This week we sit down with Vehicle Artist and TNGS winner Paul Dalessi from Foundry 42 and take a Behind-the-Scenes look at the making of the Star Citizen Alpha 2.0 demo at CitizenCon.

5.title: Model Flight
5.plot: This week we chat with Pete and John about upcoming changes to the flight model, and check in with the audio team at F42 about their work on the Starmap.

6.title: Movin' on Up...
6.plot: This week we check in with Tyler Witkin about working in QA, and take a Behind the Scenes look at our upcoming new office for the LA team.
